=== cmd 0: [dev anvil --help] ===
Manage local anvil node

Manage a local anvil node for testing deployments with CreateX factory automatically deployed.

Usage: treb dev anvil [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  start    Start local anvil node
  stop     Stop local anvil node
  restart  Restart local anvil node
  status   Show anvil status
  logs     Show anvil logs
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --no-color
          Disable colored output (also respected via NO_COLOR env var)

      --non-interactive
          Skip interactive prompts (also enabled via TREB_NON_INTERACTIVE=1, CI=true, or non-TTY
          stdin/stdout)

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

Use "treb dev anvil [command] --help" for more information about a command.
